sequenceDiagram
	participant A as Alice
	participant M as MadHatter
	participant W as Wonderland
	A->>A: 1- create a credential keypair
	M->>M: 2- create a issuer keypair
	M->>W: 2a- publish the verification key
	A->>M: 3- send a credential signature request
	M->>A: 4- sign and send back the credential
	A->>A: 5- aggregate the signed credentials
	A--xW: 6- anonymously show the credential proof
	W->>W: 7- anyone can verify the proof
